<section class="section testimonials-section" id="testimonials">
  <div class="container relative">
    
    <!-- Background glow -->
    <div class="testimonial-glow"></div>

    <div class="testimonial-header">
      <h2>Trusted by those who <span class="gradient-text">know.</span></h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle muted">Built by founders, for founders.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonial-grid">
      
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="testimonial-card glass-panel">
        <div class="quote-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="testimonial-quote">"We built Ordomation because we were tired of spending our weekends sorting through email attachments and matching them with bank exports. It's the tool we desperately needed for our own businesses."</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar placeholder-avatar">
            <span class="initial">T</span>
          </div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <h4 class="author-name">Thue Tonnesen</h4>
            <span class="author-role muted">Co-Founder</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="testimonial-card glass-panel">
        <div class="quote-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="testimonial-quote">"The accuracy of the data extraction is what sets this apart. It doesn't just grab a random number; it understands context, distinguishing VAT from total amounts perfectly. It's basically bulletproof."</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar placeholder-avatar">
            <span class="initial">J</span>
          </div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <h4 class="author-name">Joachim Ovesen</h4>
            <span class="author-role muted">Co-Founder</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="testimonial-card glass-panel">
        <div class="quote-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="testimonial-quote">"I used to dread the end of the quarter. Now I just forward my emails when they arrive and forget about it. When my accountant asks for the documentation, I just share a single perfectly organized folder."</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar placeholder-avatar">
             <span class="initial">M</span>
          </div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <h4 class="author-name">Mikkel</h4>
            <span class="author-role muted">SME Owner (Beta User)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials-section {
    padding: 120px 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .testimonial-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .testimonial-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px);
  }

  .testimonial-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    background: rgba(14, 14, 14, 0.6);
  }

  .testimonial-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), 
                0 0 0 1px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3) inset;
    background: rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.8);
  }

  .quote-icon {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .testimonial-quote {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    flex-grow: 1;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    padding-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .author-avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .placeholder-avatar {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-secondary), rgba(255,255,255,0.1));
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .placeholder-avatar .initial {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .author-name {
    font-size: 16px;
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
  }

  .author-role {
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .testimonial-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonial-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  import { gsap } from 'gsap';
  import { ScrollTrigger } from 'gsap/ScrollTrigger';

  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

    gsap.from('.testimonial-card', {
      scrollTrigger: {
        trigger: '.testimonial-grid',
        start: 'top 85%',
      },
      y: 30,
      opacity: 0,
      duration: 0.8,
      stagger: 0.15,
      ease: 'power3.out'
    });
  });
</script>
